      "title": "සිඩ්නි තණතීරුවේ ඉන්දියානුවෝ 185ට සීමා වෙයි",
      "url": "https://www.hirunews.lk/sports/392561/%E0%B7%83%E0%B7%92%E0%B6%A9%E0%B7%8A%E0%B6%B1%E0%B7%92-%E0%B6%AD%E0%B6%AB%E0%B6%AD%E0%B7%93%E0%B6%BB%E0%B7%94%E0%B7%80%E0%B7%9A-%E0%B6%89%E0%B6%B1%E0%B7%8A%E0%B6%AF%E0%B7%92%E0%B6%BA%E0%B7%8F%E0%B6%B1%E0%B7%94%E0%B7%80%E0%B7%9D-185%E0%B6%A7-%E0%B7%83%E0%B7%93%E0%B6%B8%E0%B7%8F-%E0%B7%80%E0%B7%99%E0%B6%BA%E0%B7%92",
